==English==

===Alternative forms===
* [[arsmart]] (''obsolete'')

===Etymology===
From ''[[arse]]'' + ''[[smart]]'', because the plant stings when it touches bare skin, and was often laid in beds to kill fleas.

===Pronunciation===
* {{IPA|/ˈɑːsmɑːt/|lang=en}}

